comments: Morant (MEM) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Huerter (SAC) prior to incidental follow-through contact occurring.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Fox (SAC) can't control the pass and loses control of the ball out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to the Grizzlies.
Sabonis (SAC) legally contests the driving shot attempt and incidental "high-five" contact occurs with Morant (MEM) after the release.
Jones (MEM) makes clean contact with the ball to deflect Fox's (SAC) pass attempt.
Morant (MEM) reaches across and makes contact with Monk's (SAC) body, which affects Monk's SQBR as he dribbles up the court.
Morant (MEM) legally contests Huerter's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) and Sabonis (SAC) both pursue the loose ball and incidental contact occurs as they come together at the same spot when Jackson Jr. secures the rebound.
Huerter's (SAC) hand grazes the ball and does not dislodge it before making contact with Brooks' (MEM) arm, affecting Brooks' driving shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Huerter (SAC) throws an errant inbounds pass to Fox (SAC), who can't secure it before it goes out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to the Grizzlies.
Morant (MEM) does not deliver any contact to Mitchell (SAC) before releasing back toward the perimeter for his jump shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) and Adams (MEM) mutually engage and disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Huerter (SAC) briefly rests his arm on Brooks' (MEM) shoulder and marginal contact occurs as he secures the rebound.
Huerter's (SAC) foot comes down out of bounds before he releases his pass. The Grizzlies should be awarded possession.
Jones (MEM) initiates contact with Barnes' (SAC) arm as they move up the court and affects Barnes' (SAC) SQBR.
Sabonis (SAC) and Adams (MEM) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) is firming up in Mitchell's (SAC) path and he absorbs the marginal contact to his upper thigh during the pick.
Mitchell (SAC) makes contact with Morant's (MEM) off-arm after he brings his hand underneath the ball to gather, and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) continues to move forward and delivers contact to Brooks' (MEM) front which affects his ability to defend and pursue the ball.
Sabonis (SAC) initiates contact with Adams (MEM), which affects Adams' SQBR as the pick is set.
Brooks (MEM) initiates contact with Fox's (SAC) left arm which affects his ability to make the pass.
Jackson (MEM) reaches in to attempt to steal the ball and makes some contact to Barnes' (SAC) arm as he is releasing the pass.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) commits a take foul on Sabonis (SAC).
Clarke (MEM) engages and disengages with Sabonis (SAC) off-ball and marginal contact occurs as Sabonis moves to defend the shot.
Sabonis (SAC) does not establish himself in a legal guarding position and delivers contact to Morant's (MEM) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Jones (MEM) commits a take foul on Monk (SAC).
Konchar (MEM) takes more than 5 seconds to release his inbounds pass.
Fox (SAC) jumps toward and makes contact with Morant's (MEM) body, which affects his ability to follow-through on the jump shot attempt.
Morant (MEM) steps over the free throw line prior to the ball touching the rim. A lane violation is correctly called.

Morant (MEM) initiates illegal contact with Fox (SAC) as he attempts to get to the pass. The contact occurs prior to Fox returning to the ground and starting his upward shooting motion, and a personal foul is correctly assessed.
